I have an idea for TNTL:

Perhaps everyone who tries to make the person laugh can make bets that they can get the person to laugh with a stipulation such as:

1. I can make the person laugh in 10 seconds
Or
2. I can make the person laugh in 5 words or less
Or
3. I can make the person laugh by using only 1 prop.

And for every time they fail their own challenge, they get a point. Whoever has the most points loses and must suffer a punishment whether it’s eating a hot pepper or getting something nasty dumped over their head.

You can call it “Nothin’ but Bet”

Just a thought for a future TNTL! Love the content everyone!
